00:22:08,600 --> 00:22:11,800
The Kramer office?

246
00:22:12,920 --> 00:22:14,640
It was a good bomb.

247
00:22:14,760 --> 00:22:17,560
- But I never meant to kill anybody.
- Really?

248
00:22:17,680 --> 00:22:20,800
You bombed the Pinder house at 4 a.m.,
with six people there.

249
00:22:20,920 --> 00:22:24,120
